- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a novel probabilistic technique for variable name recovery using neural networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper uses machine learning techniques for variable name recovery. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as decompilers are commonly used in security research to analyze malware and other malicious software.
